'''筏罗诃'''（'''Varaha'''，{{lang-sa|वराह}}），又稱'''[[猪头大圣|猪头大圣]]'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://okapi.books.com.tw/article/11760 |title=【大叔們的書袋｜BOOK 04】人類碰上豬，總是往一個方向前進──餐桌 |access-date=2020-04-11 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107065922/https://okapi.books.com.tw/article/11760 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>《道家文化研究24卷》.陳鼓應.上海古籍出版社，第248頁。「此外則有香山、雪山二大聖，豬頭、象鼻二大聖，雄威、華光二大聖。」</ref>
<ref>《福建省壽寧縣閭山梨園教科儀本彙編》，第108頁 。「則有香山、雪山二大聖，豬頭、象鼻，不過只三十三字金輪穢跡咒也。」</ref>，[[梵文|梵文]]，意为公猪，[[印度教|印度教]]大神[[毗湿奴|毗湿奴]]10种[[化身|化身]]中的第三种。妖魔[[金目|金目]]（Hiranyaksha）把大地拖入海底，毗湿奴即化身为公猪筏罗诃以拯救大地。经过1000年争斗，筏罗诃杀死[[阿修羅王|阿修羅王]][[金輪|金輪]]，用它的獠牙从海底捞出大地。筏罗诃之像或为公猪，或为猪头人身<ref name="Geer2008">{{cite book|author=Alexandra Anna Enrica van der Geer|title=Animals in Stone: Indian Mammals Sculptured Through Time|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=oQ3quxh9gsgC&pg=PA402|accessdate=1 January 2013|year=2008|publisher=BRILL|isbn=978-90-04-16819-0|pages=401–6|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060119/http://books.google.com/books?id=oQ3quxh9gsgC&pg=PA402|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Snead1989">{{cite book|author=Stella Snead|title=Animals in Four Worlds: Sculptures from India|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Jb1Wa_SRNewC&pg=PA147|accessdate=1 January 2013|date=7 September 1989|publisher=University of Chicago Press|isbn=978-0-226-76726-0|page=39|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921063216/http://books.google.com/books?id=Jb1Wa_SRNewC&pg=PA147|dead-url=no}}</ref>

